Package org.concordion.cubano.driver.web

Class ChainExpectedConditions

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.concordion.cubano.driver.web.ChainExpectedConditions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.function.Function<org.openqa.selenium.WebDriver,java.lang.Boolean>, org.openqa.selenium.support.ui.ExpectedCondition<java.lang.Boolean>

    public class ChainExpectedConditions
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.openqa.selenium.support.ui.ExpectedCondition<java.lang.Boolean>

    Designed to work with WebDriverWait when you have multiple condition to check on a page.

    Each condition will be checked in turn until until they all passed or the calling Wait method times out.

    Once a condition has passed it will not be checked again.
